this project is the copy of medium but with advance ai support  , with features that allow users to write and post blogs , (only admin can feature can also be done )
-features 
=> Home page
1. srch 
2. topic selection(filter)
3. write btn
4. authentication
5. trending topics on right side

=> each blog page 
1. blog main img
2. author details and published  on
3. like comment and social media a/c
4. search functionality (srch via blog or user name)

=> write btn functionality
1. if not login then show login page 
2. authentication via email and password and sign up via name email and password (google oauth facility also there)
3. after authentication specific users page will be shown with the login image and notification option beside the write button.
4. user option (profile,dashboard, settings, sign out)
   
=>Users profile page
1. Blogs published 
2. username and profile pic
3. no of blogs and no of reads
4. edit profile option
5. joining date


=> settings page or the edit profile page
-> leftmost section
1. Dashboard -> blogs , notifications , write 
2. settings  -> edit profile -> change password
   
-> middle section
1. image edit section

-> rightmost section
1. name, email
2. username
3. bio-with limit chars
4. adding social media handlers ( yt, facebook, insta, X, github, etc)
5. update butn


